me.pagekite.glen3b.library.bukkit.reflection

Class SafeReflection

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.pagekite.glen3b.library.bukkit.reflection.SafeReflection

  • public final class SafeReflection
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides wrapper utility methods intended to be able to do reflection without throwing exceptions. Unless otherwise noted, methods in this class will, in the event of catching an exception, print the stack trace of that exception and return null.
    Author:
    Glen Husman
